      <title>VM虚拟机安装kali linux系统</title>
      <link href="/posts/66666/"/>
      <url>/posts/66666/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="准备工具"><a href="#准备工具" class="headerlink" title="准备工具"></a><strong>准备工具</strong></h1><p>1.VMware workstation16虚拟机安装包：<a href="https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/CK4ZyvNtFt7">阿里云盘</a> 提取码: 2abl</p><p>2.kali系统官方ios镜像：<a href="https://www.kali.org/get-kali/#kali-bare-metal">点我跳转</a>  根据自己电脑操作系统选择不同的版本。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/2.png" alt=" "></p><h1 id="安装VM虚拟机"><a href="#安装VM虚拟机" class="headerlink" title="安装VM虚拟机"></a><strong>安装VM虚拟机</strong></h1><ul><li>打开下载好的安装包按照提示完成安装，在最后一步点击许可证在下面选一个激活码填上激活VM虚拟机。</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ZF71R-DMX85-08DQY-8YMNC-PPHV8</span><br><span class="line">ZF3R0-FHED2-M80TY-8QYGC-NPKYF</span><br><span class="line">YF390-0HF8P-M81RQ-2DXQE-M2UT6</span><br><span class="line">FA1M0-89YE3-081TQ-AFNX9-NKUC0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装Kali-Linux系统"><a href="#安装Kali-Linux系统" class="headerlink" title="安装Kali Linux系统"></a><strong>安装Kali Linux系统</strong></h1><hr><p>title: Kali从入门到入狱系列<br>tags:</p><ul><li>kali</li><li>虚拟机<br>categories:</li><li>教程</li><li>虚拟机<br>cover: ‘<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/1.png&#39;">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/1.png&#39;</a><br>abbrlink: 66666<br>date: 2022-04-20 12:47:07<br>updated:</li></ul><hr><h1 id="准备工具-1"><a href="#准备工具-1" class="headerlink" title="准备工具"></a><strong>准备工具</strong></h1><p>1.VMware workstation16虚拟机安装包：<a href="https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/CK4ZyvNtFt7">阿里云盘</a> 提取码: 2abl</p><p>2.kali系统官方ios镜像：<a href="https://www.kali.org/get-kali/#kali-bare-metal">点我跳转</a>  根据自己电脑操作系统选择不同的版本。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/2.png" alt=" "></p><h1 id="安装VM虚拟机-1"><a href="#安装VM虚拟机-1" class="headerlink" title="安装VM虚拟机"></a><strong>安装VM虚拟机</strong></h1><ul><li>打开下载好的安装包按照提示完成安装，在最后一步点击许可证在下面选一个激活码填上激活VM虚拟机。</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ZF71R-DMX85-08DQY-8YMNC-PPHV8</span><br><span class="line">ZF3R0-FHED2-M80TY-8QYGC-NPKYF</span><br><span class="line">YF390-0HF8P-M81RQ-2DXQE-M2UT6</span><br><span class="line">FA1M0-89YE3-081TQ-AFNX9-NKUC0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装Kali-Linux系统-1"><a href="#安装Kali-Linux系统-1" class="headerlink" title="安装Kali Linux系统"></a><strong>安装Kali Linux系统</strong></h1><blockquote><p>选择新建虚拟机</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/3.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/4.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/5.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/6.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/7.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>自己选择合适的大小</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/8.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/9.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>根据自己的电脑配置合理选择，不懂就默认</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/10.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/11.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/12.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/13.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/14.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/15.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/16.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/17.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>域名留空继续</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/18.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>输入自定义用户名</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/19.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/20.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>设置用户密码</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/21.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/22.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/23.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/24.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/25.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/26.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/27.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/28.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/29.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/30.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/31.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/32.png" alt=" "><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/33.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>输入刚刚设置的用户名和密码</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/34.png" alt=" "></p><blockquote><p>进入系统桌面</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shilinniao/cdn/img/kali/35.png" alt=" "></p><p>至此Kali系统就安装好了。</p>]]></content>
      
      
